page.title: 13MODERN VILLAGE
page.content: My name is Jane Pickthall I live in Osnaburgh Court in Dairsie in a timber framed house.It was built in 1974. We have a garage for one car. I live with my mum,dad,sister Claire and Henry our dog. We have two gardens one at the front and one at the back. Our back garden is fenced all round because there is a field next door and Henry might escape. Our front garden does not have and hedges or fences only a lawn and flower beds. In our house we have three bedrooms,a kitchen bathroom and dinette. Pauline lives next door. Her house is exactly the same but she has two split bedrooms,a diningroom and a living room. Outside she has not got a shed or patio and she does not have her back garden fenced in.
